### ğŸ” Match + Pattern Example ###
let command = "status"

match command:
    "start" => print("Starting system...")
    "stop" => print("Stopping system...")
    "status" => print("System online.")
    _ => print("Unknown command.")

### ğŸ” While Loop ###
